00:42.920 --> 00:45.037
Do you think the world was fixed before?

00:45.280 --> 00:46.280
No, of course not.

00:46.600 --> 00:48.796
It takes something like this
to make you realise

00:49.520 --> 00:50.670
how everything is ruined.

00:53.400 --> 00:55.631
Are you referring to the relationship
with your wife?

00:57.960 --> 00:58.960
What I did...

01:02.400 --> 01:04.391
What they asked me to do...

01:09.160 --> 01:10.389
it changed everything.

01:11.880 --> 01:14.270
I'm wondering,
when you say the world is broken

01:14.320 --> 01:15.320
maybe...

01:16.120 --> 01:20.160
you're referring to something
that is broken inside of you?

01:23.120 --> 01:25.401
It's like you haven't listened
to a word I've been saying.

01:27.520 --> 01:28.749
What I did...

01:32.200 --> 01:33.350
it can't be undone.

01:36.160 --> 01:38.117
And as a direct consequence

01:41.640 --> 01:43.040
the world has changed.

01:45.720 --> 01:47.598
Everything's changed, because of what I did.

01:51.040 --> 01:52.040
That's time.

01:54.840 --> 01:55.840
Good.

01:56.120 --> 01:57.120
Um...

